NO LIGHT VERSION FOR BETTER GAMEPLAY.

The final version of White Castle. I took out lighting because it caused some glitches and lagg. enjoy this crazy map with almost a infinity of secrets and  surprises!!!

Contains things like :
Fully working Cannons
mine field
Traps
Spooky grave yard
Low gravity room
knife fight room
Teleports
Secret doors

And much much much more!
